scripts.gen: rm -rf ./api/ && docker run -u $(id -u ${USER}):$(id -g ${USER}) --rm -v ${PWD}:/local openapitools/openapi-generator-cli generate -i /local/openapi.json -g typescript -o /local/api/ --additional-properties=usePromises=true,paramNaming=original,modelPropertyNaming=original,enumPropertyNaming=original
